description: Are you ready for a whimsical adventure through Wonderland? Well, get ready to fall down the rabbit hole with the Disney Alice in Wonderland A Very Merry Unbirthday to You Mini Backpack! This fabulous pack features a playful scene of the Mad Hatter, The Dormouse, and March Hare serving up tea while balancing in a teacup. It's almost like you're right there with them, sipping on Earl Grey and munching on a biscuit.Crafted with vegan leather (polyurethane), this mini backpack is not only adorable, but it's also eco-friendly. You can strut around with ease, not worrying about the bag weighing you down while you strut your stuff. Additionally, the bag has adjustable shoulder straps, sturdy metal hardware, and features that will knock your socks off, like embroidered, applique, debossed, and printed details. Whether you're headed to a tea party, a concert, or simply running errands, this backpack is the perfect way to add some whimsy to your ensemble.How delightful would it be to take this backpack on a fun-filled journey through Wonderland? Can't you just picture it now - a world where everything is topsy-turvy and nothing is quite what it seems? Pair it up with a frilly dress, some funky leggings, and a pair of brightly colored boots, and you're just about ready to join Alice and the rest of the crew. So go ahead, put on the Mad Hatter's hat, sip some piping hot tea, and make every day an unbirthday with this playful pack!Here are a few more details you'll love about the Disney Alice in Wonderland A Very Merry Unbirthday to You Mini Backpack:- The coordinating pattern of the inside lining fabric is an adorable, whimsical touch that really takes things up a notch.- The dimensions of the backpack are made to fit your necessities without feeling too bulky or heavy.- This is an officially licensed Disney product, so you know you're getting the real deal. Don't be fooled by any imitations, because they simply won't measure up to the magic of this mini backpack.Product DetailsProduct type: Mini BackpackLicense: Alice in WonderlandManufacturer: LoungeflySpecificaties Gewicht: Ongeveer 720 gram (25 ounces) Land van herkomst: China Materialen: Kunstleer (polyurethaan) SKU: WDBK1651GTIN: 671803370661
